name: Sam Brannan Park Tennis Courts
description: Sam Brannan Park Tennis Courts is a place to play pickleball in Yuba City, CA. There are 6 outdoor asphalt courts. These are dedicated courts with permanent lines and nets. Players have access to food, restrooms, water, and lights. The courts are free.

name: Willow Glen Care Center
description: Willow Glen Care Center is one of the most popular places to play pickleball in Yuba City, CA. There is 1 indoor court. The lines are permanent, but you'll need to bring your own net. The court is free. Players have access to lights.
